profile:
One Landscape Design & Build is a design and build landscaping company that has operated in Peterborough, Kawartha's & Durham Region since 1999, and now, in addition we also operate in the GTA Region and beautiful Muskoka Highlands. Our staff allows us to offer full landscaping services such as consultation, design and build using interlocking stone, paving, natural stone retaining walls, natural stone accents, manufactured retaining walls (Oaks, Unilock and Hansen), flagstone (random or square cut) concrete walkways, patios, decks, steps, pool decks, pool construction, water features of all shapes and sizes. We also have an in-shop carpentry crew to ensure seamless completion of all fence, deck, and wood structures. In addition, we also provide excavation, grading and sod services upon request.

At One Landscape, we are we dedicated to making your landscape vision a reality. We will walk you through your entire project from start to finish beginning with design consultation and exchange of ideas and visions for your project. We then will put together a free no-obligation quote to meet your landscape needs and budget.

We are helping to beautify our regions by offering both residential, commercial, and industrial landscaping services to provide excellent quality, eye pleasing and remarkable landscapes at a fair price. 

At One Landscape we pride ourselves on our array of professional services, spectacular design and skilled staff to complete all our projects. It is through our valued customers that we are able to define our success in the past and goals for the future.
services:

profile:
Under the Sun Ecological Landscaping is a full service Landscape Contractor and Design company providing design, installation and maintenance to the Greater Toronto Area, Oshawa and Peterborough.
We specialize in ecological, chemical-free, organic landscaping including: organic gardens, carpentry and stone work.
service_area: Greater Toronto Area, Riverdale, Scarborough, Annex, North York, Markham, Beaches, Pickering, Ajax, Oshawa
services:
Full service Landscape design and installation. 
Stone work:  flagstone patios, stone facing, retaining walls, water features.
Interlock:  driveways, paths, patios and more.
Carpentry:  decks, fences, screens, gates, gazebos, trellises, steps and more.
Gardens:  Vegetable gardens, edible landscaping, low maintenance gardens, native gardens, butterfly gardens, rain gardens and more.
Irrigation:  automatic irrigation systems, drip, spray and low flow irrigation.
Organic Landscaping Toronto, Oshawa and Peterborough
